ng Kong!"},{"pid":"011349d6fa1521c611aac3e1d458c0b705ae1eb2","tid":1548060,"uid":260495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c90c24fdc10555d3bf5ea5244960e8784ca70534","tid":1548060,"uid":260495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"有手足比人圍 求救！<br />\n<br />\n有無人係尖東連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c33f6960439194802b81d3f8381d511113fd79af","tid":1548060,"uid":260495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fca3d3c13b257e09290539949cc2b8712ae996b9","tid":1548060,"uid":260495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"搵到相！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNim7Di.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNim7Di.png&h=c33f90a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f69170bd0d1304626d7c21d7060e5e00756478c7","tid":1548060,"uid":320472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"係依班人清的...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/youthcleaning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyouthcleaning&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=1efe505b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/youthcleaning</a><br />\n<br />\n我無眼睇，<br />\n愈睇愈x 嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry